													<p class="mt-4" style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 24px; color: #777777;">
														Please complete the payment by filling in all the required fields carefully. Ensure that you enter the name and phone number associated with the EVC Plus, ZAAD, and Sahal Mobile Services you are using to successfully finalize the transaction.


													</p>
												</td>
											</tr>
											<div class="row justify-content-center mb-4 radio-group">
